  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/misc-gadgets/\" rel=\"tag\">精彩杂录</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/10/ang-lee-set-to-helm-3d-boxing-film-re-create-classic-60s-and/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/08/ang-lee-boxing-3d-2013-08-09-01.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在执导了 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/03/11/must-see-hdtv-march-11th-17th/\">Life of Pi</a> 之后，奥斯卡小金人得主李安的下一步计划是什么呢？日前在接受 Deadline Hollywood 采访的时候他就给出了答案。据悉李大导演的下一部作品将把目光聚焦到六、七十年代的拳坛，包括 Ali 和 Frazier、Hearns 和 Duran 等传奇拳手间的较量将会成为该影片的主旋律。值得一提的是，李安已经决定用 3D 方式拍摄这部作品，之前在 Avatar、Life of Pi 中大出风头的 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2010/04/10/resident-evil-afterlife-trailer-promises-james-camerons-camera/\">Cameron / Pace Fusion</a> 3D 技术很有可能会再度被他选中。到目前为止影片的具体情节和技术细节还没有被公布，但就过去的表现来看，李导应该不会让我们失望吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/08/09/ang-lee-set-to-helm-3d-boxing-film-re-create-classic-60s-and/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/aug/09/ang-lee-3d-boxing-movie\" target=\"_blank\">The Guardian</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.deadline.com/2013/08/ang-lee-to-next-helm-3d-film-with-classic-boxing-battles-including-ali-frazier/\" target=\"_blank\">Deadline Hollywood</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/10/ang-lee-set-to-helm-3d-boxing-film-re-create-classic-60s-and/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20691388/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/10/ang-lee-set-to-helm-3d-boxing-film-re-create-classic-60s-and/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
